pageContext.claim: “Just returning from the Great State of Minnesota where we had an incredible rally with 9,000 people, and at least 10,000 who could not get in - I will return! Congratulations to @PeteStauber who is loved and respected in Minnesota!”
pageContext.analysis: While there was a wait to enter the rally, no reports found 10,000 people couldn't get in. Plus, Minnesota Public Radio noted the rally was "more than 8,000 people" not 9,000.
